    "1400606": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Wriothesley",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Ielmini",
                    "T": "Your Grace, Your Grace!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "What's the matter?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ielmini",
                    "T": "We couldn't find any Society members in the other areas. It also seems like none of the equipment in those rooms were ever used — all the signs of wear and tear are fake."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ielmini",
                    "T": "The limescale, the layers of dust... they were all deliberately added."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ielmini",
                    "T": "We also investigated the members' residences, and weren't able to find anything. Their neighbors all say that they haven't returned home for ages."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Oh... Is that right..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "They're gone? That could only mean..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Society put a lot of effort into building a front."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Their real headquarters are elsewhere."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Indeed. As long as he allowed Society members to mingle with others, even with threats of censure, Dougier knew that he could not stop all of his members from speaking out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Meanwhile, this marvelous \"gathering place\" will lose all of its value as soon as a whistleblower sounds the alarm."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "So instead of being his real base, this is just an elaborate performance. The rest areas, the fancy equipment, even the members that we saw... they were merely a part of the front."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "And only the most docile and well-trained members were selected as his \"performers.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But then... where can we actually find him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Let me think..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Dougier must be holding all the rest of his members in another place. And if the overseer of my Fortress Guard has never alerted me to anything of the sort..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "He must be in Dougier's pocket."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's go find him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He can tell us where the real headquarters are."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "I'm of the same mind. Let's go. You too, follow me."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
