    "1400609": {
        "Desc": "Go after the Beret Society members that escaped",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Wyler",
                    "T": "Those blasted guards!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gouzien",
                    "T": "*panting*... *panting*..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Did Dougier send you? Why did you attack that guard?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wyler",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "C'mon, it's time to talk! Can't you see that he's trying to help!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "I will take your cooperation into consideration when it comes time to hand out sentences."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wyler",
                    "T": "Mr. Dougier, h—he... didn't want this guy to expose our true location..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wyler",
                    "T": "We were just about to dispose of him when you caught up to us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "So, in other words, your headquarters should be this way?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gouzien",
                    "T": "Y—Yes, it's just down this way. You'll make it there once you've seen and passed through a large drainage pipe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Now that's more like it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Guards, take them away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Let's go. It's about time that we find out what Dougier's really after."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
